import { Routes, Route, useLocation } from 'react-router-dom';
import { AnimatePresence, motion } from 'framer-motion';
import Calculator from './Components/Calculator';
import Liverates from './Components/Liverates';
import About from './Components/About';

const pageVariants = {
  initial: { x: "100vw", opacity: 0 },
  animate: { x: 0, opacity: 1, transition: { type: "spring", stiffness: 100 } },
  exit: { x: "-100vw", opacity: 0, transition: { ease: "easeInOut", duration: 0.3 } }
};

function AnimatedRoutes() {
  const location = useLocation();

  return (
    <AnimatePresence mode="wait">
      <Routes location={location} key={location.pathname}>
        <Route
          path="/"
          element={<motion.div variants={pageVariants} initial="initial" animate="animate" exit="exit"><Calculator /></motion.div>}
        />
        <Route
          path="/about"
          element={<motion.div variants={pageVariants} initial="initial" animate="animate" exit="exit"><About /></motion.div>}
        />
        <Route
          path="/liverates"
          element={<motion.div variants={pageVariants} initial="initial" animate="animate" exit="exit"><Liverates /></motion.div>}
        />
      </Routes>
    </AnimatePresence>
  );
}

export default AnimatedRoutes;

âœ… 1. Modify AnimatedRoutes.jsx to Track Direction

Hume ek state (direction) maintain karni padegi taaki hum yeh decide kar sake ki next page left se aaye ya right se.

jsx
import { Routes, Route, useLocation } from 'react-router-dom';
import { AnimatePresence, motion } from 'framer-motion';
import { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import Calculator from './Calculator';
import Liverates from './Liverates';

const pageVariants = (direction) => ({
  initial: { x: direction === "left" ? "100vw" : "-100vw", opacity: 0 },
  animate: { x: 0, opacity: 1, transition: { type: "spring", stiffness: 100 } },
  exit: { x: direction === "left" ? "-100vw" : "100vw", opacity: 0, transition: { ease: "easeInOut", duration: 0.3 } }
});

function AnimatedRoutes() {
  const location = useLocation();
  const [direction, setDirection] = useState("left"); // Default direction

  useEffect(() => {
    if (location.pathname === "/") setDirection("right");
    else setDirection("left");
  }, [location.pathname]);

  return (
    <AnimatePresence mode="wait">
      <Routes location={location} key={location.pathname}>
        <Route
          path="/"
          element={
            <motion.div variants={pageVariants(direction)} initial="initial" animate="animate" exit="exit">
              <Calculator />
            </motion.div>
          }
        />
        <Route
          path="/liverates"
          element={
            <motion.div variants={pageVariants(direction)} initial="initial" animate="animate" exit="exit">
              <Liverates />
            </motion.div>
          }
        />
      </Routes>
    </AnimatePresence>
  );
}

export default AnimatedRoutes;

jsx
import { useState, useEffect } from "react";

const Liverates = () => {
  const [baseCurrency, setBaseCurrency] = useState("USD"); // Default currency
  const [exchangeRates, setExchangeRates] = useState({});
  const [currencies, setCurrencies] = useState([]);

  // API call function
  const fetchExchangeRate = async (fromCurrency) => {
    try {
      const res = await fetch(`https://v6.exchangerate-api.com/v6/3d3133a5c069b81679c24d0d/latest/${fromCurrency}`);
      const data = await res.json();
      setExchangeRates(data.conversion_rates || {});
      setCurrencies(Object.keys(data.conversion_rates || {}));
    } catch (error) {
      console.error("Error fetching exchange rate:", error);
    }
  };

  // Fetch rates whenever baseCurrency changes
  useEffect(() => {
    fetchExchangeRate(baseCurrency);
  }, [baseCurrency]);

  return (
    <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4">
      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Live Exchange Rates</h2>

      {/* Dropdown for selecting base currency */}
      <div className="flex justify-center mb-4">
        <label className="mr-2 font-semibold">Select Base Currency:</label>
        <select
          value={baseCurrency}
          onChange={(e) => setBaseCurrency(e.target.value)}
          className="border p-2 rounded"
        >
          {currencies.map((currency) => (
            <option key={currency} value={currency}>
              {currency}
            </option>
          ))}
        </select>
      </div>

      {/* Exchange Rate Table */}
      <div className="overflow-x-auto">
        <table className="min-w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300">
          <thead>
            <tr className="bg-gray-200">
              <th className="border p-2">Currency</th>
              <th className="border p-2">Exchange Rate</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {Object.entries(exchangeRates).map(([currency, rate]) => (
              <tr key={currency} className="border">
                <td className="border p-2">{currency}</td>
                <td className="border p-2">{rate.toFixed(4)}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default Liverates;

import { useState, useEffect } from "react";

// Currency Code â†’ Country Code Mapping
const currencyToCountry = {
  USD: "us",
  INR: "in",
  EUR: "eu",
  GBP: "gb",
  JPY: "jp",
  AUD: "au",
  CAD: "ca",
  CHF: "ch",
  CNY: "cn",
  HKD: "hk",
  SGD: "sg",
  NZD: "nz",
  SEK: "se",
  KRW: "kr",
  ZAR: "za",
  BRL: "br",
  RUB: "ru",
  MXN: "mx",
  IDR: "id",
  TRY: "tr",
  SAR: "sa",
  NOK: "no",
  TWD: "tw",

const Liverates = () => {
  const [baseCurrency, setBaseCurrency] = useState("USD"); // Default base currency
  const [exchangeRates, setExchangeRates] = useState({});
  const [currencies, setCurrencies] = useState([]);
  const [baseAmount, setBaseAmount] = useState(1); // Default amount = 1

  // Fetch exchange rates from API
  const fetchExchangeRate = async (fromCurrency) => {
    try {
      const res = await fetch(`https://v6.exchangerate-api.com/v6/3d3133a5c069b81679c24d0d/latest/${fromCurrency}`);
      const data = await res.json();
      setExchangeRates(data.conversion_rates || {});
      setCurrencies(Object.keys(data.conversion_rates || {}));
    } catch (error) {
      console.error("Error fetching exchange rate:", error);
    }
  };

  // Fetch when baseCurrency changes
  useEffect(() => {
    fetchExchangeRate(baseCurrency);
  }, [baseCurrency]);

  return (
    <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4">
      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Live Exchange Rates</h2>

      {/* Select Base Currency */}
      <div className="flex justify-center items-center gap-4 mb-4">
        <label className="font-semibold">Base Currency:</label>
        <select
          value={baseCurrency}
          onChange={(e) => setBaseCurrency(e.target.value)}
          className="border p-2 rounded"
        >
          {currencies.map((currency) => (
            <option key={currency} value={currency}>{currency}</option>
          ))}
        </select>

        {/* Enter Base Amount */}
        <input
          type="number"
          value={baseAmount}
          onChange={(e) => setBaseAmount(e.target.value)}
          className="border p-2 rounded w-24 text-center"
          min="1"
        />
      </div>

      {/* Exchange Rate Table */}
      <div className="overflow-x-auto">
        <table className="min-w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300">
          <thead>
            <tr className="bg-gray-200">
              <th className="border p-2">Currency</th>
              <th className="border p-2">Exchange Rate</th>
              <th className="border p-2">{baseAmount} {baseCurrency} Value</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {Object.entries(exchangeRates).map(([currency, rate]) => {
              const countryCode = currencyToCountry[currency] || "un"; // Default "un" if not found
              return (
                <tr key={currency} className="border">
                  <td className="border text-2xl text-center text-CalcGreenText p-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <img
                      alt={currency}
                      src={`https://flagcdn.com/w40/${countryCode}.png`}
                      className="w-6 h-4"
                    />
                    {currency}
                  </td>
                  <td className="border text-2xl text-center text-CalcGreenText p-2">{rate.toFixed(4)}</td>
                  <td className="border text-2xl text-center text-CalcGreenText p-2">{(rate * baseAmount).toFixed(4)}</td> 
                </tr>
              );
            })}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default Liverates;

localStorage.setItem("conversionHistory", JSON.stringify(updatedHistory));
}
}, [value1, exchangeRate]);

setSelectedCountry(selectedCountry2);

setInputOneCurrency(InputOneCurrency2);

setValue1(value2);

setHistory([]);
